quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,38,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU MA LEKUM ‘IDHA KILE LEKUM ENFIRU FI SEBILI ELLAHI ETHTHAKALTUM ‘ILAL-’ERDI ‘EREDITUM BIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA MINEL-’AHIRETI FEMA META’UL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ILLA KALILUN
  9,39,‘ILLA TENFIRU JU’ADHDHIBKUM ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN WE JESTEBDIL KAWMÆN GAJREKUM WE LA TEDURRUHU SHEJ’ÆN WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  9,40,‘ILLA TENSURUHU FEKAD NESEREHU ELLAHU ‘IDH ‘EHREXHEHUL-LEDHINE KEFERU THANIJE ETHNEJNI ‘IDH HUMA FIL-GARI ‘IDH JEKULU LISAHIBIHI LA TEHZEN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ME’ANA FE’ENZELEL-LAHU SEKINETEHU ‘ALEJHI WE ‘EJJEDEHU BIXHUNUDIN LEM TEREWHA WE XHE’ALE KELIMETEL-LED
  9,41,ENFIRU HIFAFÆN WE THIKALÆN WE XHAHIDU BI’EMWALIKUM WE ‘ENFUSIKUM FI SEBILI ELLAHI DHALIKUM HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  9,42,LEW KANE ‘AREDÆN KARIBÆN WE SEFERÆN KASIDÆN LATTEBA’UKE WE LEKIN BA’UDET ‘ALEJHIMU ESH-SHUKKATU WE SEJEHLIFUNE BILLAHI LEW ESTETA’NA LEHAREXHNA ME’AKUM JUHLIKUNE ‘ENFUSEHUM WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE